Examples:

```
# Format the range ``A1:C1`` with bold text
# and format the range ``A2:C2`` a font size of 16

formats = [
    {
        "range": "A1:C1",
        "format": {
            "textFormat": {
                "bold": True,
            },
        },
    },
    {
        "range": "A2:C2",
        "format": {
            "textFormat": {
                "fontSize": 16,
            },
        },
    },
]
worksheet.batch_format(formats)
```

